'''索馬里蘭共和国的外交關係'''是由其{{link-en|索馬利蘭外交部|Ministry of Foreign Affairs (Somaliland)|外交部}}負責<ref name="ministers">[http://www.somalilandgov.com/government.htm Council of Ministers] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20010107213900/http://www.somalilandgov.com/government.htm |date=2001-01-07 }}. Government of Somaliland.</ref>。

[[索馬利蘭共和國|索馬利蘭共和國]]雖已自行宣布[[独立国家|獨立]]為一[[共和國|共和國]]，但不被國際社會承认為一国家<ref name="NYT">Lacey, Marc (5 June 2006). [http://www.nytimes.com/2006/06/05/world/africa/05somaliland.html The Signs Say Somaliland, but the World Says Somalia] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/5z4NpH8Zd?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/06/05/world/africa/05somaliland.html |date=20110530150728 |dateformat=iso }}. ''The New York Times''. Retrieved 2010-05-25.</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.un.org/webcast/pdfs/unia991.pdf |title=UN in Action: Reforming Somaliland's Judiciary |format=PDF |date= |accessdate=2012-05-29 |archive-date=2009-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090422175529/http://www.un.org/webcast/pdfs/unia991.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而是被[[有限承认国家列表|公認]]為[[索马里联邦共和国|索马里联邦共和国]]的[[索马里联邦成员州|联邦成员州]]之一<ref name="Tupmorttsep">{{cite news|title=The UK Prime Minister's Office Reply To The "Somaliland E-Petition"|url=http://www.somalilandtimes.net/sl/2006/270/3.shtml|accessdate=23 April 2014|newspaper=Somaliland Times|date=22 March 2007|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160321062435/http://www.somalilandtimes.net/sl/2006/270/3.shtml|archive-date=2016-03-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；現階段，國際社會的立場為支持索馬里政府、及該國領土的完整和主權<ref name="Cosgmsos"/>。

由於索馬里蘭的政治地位存在争议，該國长期沒有與任何國家進行官方往來；索馬里蘭政府現行外交政策的首要目標是爭取國際承認為主權国家和維持国家穩定，其次則為鼓勵外國援助或投資<ref>[http://somalilandpress.com/chinese-delegation-returns-to-somaliland-for-investment-13417 Chinese delegation returns to Somaliland for investment] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140214192725/http://somalilandpress.com/chinese-delegation-returns-to-somaliland-for-investment-13417 |date=2014-02-14 }}. ''Somaliland Press'' (26 April 2010). Retrieved 2010-05-25.</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
索馬里蘭與[[衣索比亞|衣索比亞]]<ref name="Future recognition" />、[[吉布地|吉布地]]<ref name="Djibouti" >{{cite web| title=Somaliland, Djibouti in bitter port feud| url=http://www.afrol.com/articles/23556| publisher=afrol News| accessdate=2007-07-22| archive-date=2012-02-12| archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65OZFZcqf?url=http://www.afrol.com/articles/23556| dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[比利時|比利時]]<ref name="Future recognition" >{{cite web|title=Somaliland closer to recognition by Ethiopia|url=http://www.afrol.com/articles/25633|publisher=Afrol News|accessdate=2007-07-06|archive-date=2012-02-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65OUeUIkg?url=http://www.afrol.com/articles/25633|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[法國|法國]]<ref>{{cite news | title=France recognizes ''de facto'' Somaliland | url=http://www.lesnouvelles.org/P10_magazine/15_grandentretien/15055_mahamudsalahnur_eng.html | publisher=Les Nouvelles d'Addis | date=2008-04-08 | accessdate=2010-02-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100715224433/http://www.lesnouvelles.org/P10_magazine/15_grandentretien/15055_mahamudsalahnur_eng.html | archive-date=2010-07-15 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[加納|加納]]<ref name="Future recognition" />、[[肯亞|肯亞]]<ref>{{cite web | title=Kenyan Deputy Speaker addresses Somaliland parliament | url=http://somalilandpress.com/10344/kenyan-deputy-speaker-addresses-somaliland-parliament/ | publisher=Somaliland Press | date=2009-12-24 | accessdate=2010-01-02 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100420050150/http://somalilandpress.com/10344/kenyan-deputy-speaker-addresses-somaliland-parliament/ | archivedate=2010-04-20 }} </ref>、[[南非|南非]]<ref name="Future recognition" />、[[瑞典|瑞典]]<ref name="Future recognition" /><ref>{{cite web | title=Somaliland Diplomatic Mission in Sweden | url=http://www.somalilandembassy.se/ | accessdate=2010-04-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090510080355/http://www.somalilandembassy.se/ | archive-date=2009-05-10 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[英國|英國]]<ref name="Future recognition" /><ref>{{cite web| title=Somaliland| url=http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200304/cmhansrd/vo040204/halltext/40204h03.htm| publisher=United Kingdom Parliament| date=2004-02-04| accessdate=2007-02-23| archive-date=2021-03-13| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313195235/https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200304/cmhansrd/vo040204/halltext/40204h03.htm| dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[美國|美國]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://somalilandpress.com/press-release-the-republic-of-somailand-liaison-office-washington-dc-12868 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-02-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130404125152/http://somalilandpress.com/press-release-the-republic-of-somailand-liaison-office-washington-dc-12868 |archivedate=2013-04-04 }}</ref>保持政治上的接觸，其中衣索比亞和吉布地是索馬利亞的鄰國。2007年，索馬里蘭總統[[達希爾·雷亞萊·卡欣|達希爾·雷亞萊·卡欣]]率領代表團出席於[[烏干達|烏干達]][[坎帕拉|坎帕拉]]的{{link-en|2007年英聯邦政府首腦會議|Commonwealth Heads of Government Meeting 2007|英聯邦政府首腦會議}}；儘管索馬里蘭已申請以觀察員身份加入[[英聯邦|英聯邦]]，但申請至今仍懸而未決<ref>{{cite web | title=Somaliland on verge of observer status in the Commonwealth | url=http://www.qarannews.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=6381&Itemid=59 | publisher=Qaran News | date=2009-11-16 | accessdate=2010-02-02 | archive-date=2012-02-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120219054637/http://www.qarannews.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=6381&Itemid=59 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。索馬里蘭是[[非聯合國會員國家及民族組織|非聯合國會員國家及民族組織]]的成員國之一<ref name="#1">{{cite web |url=http://www.garoweonline.com/artman2/publish/Somalia_27/Yemen_and_Puntland_to_further_cooperation.shtml |title=Yemen and Puntland to further cooperation |publisher=Garoweonline.com |date=2010-10-12 |accessdate=2012-05-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328171433/http://www.garoweonline.com/artman2/publish/Somalia_27/Yemen_and_Puntland_to_further_cooperation.shtml |archivedate=2012-03-28 }}</ref>。

2002年，[[德國|德國]]考慮承認索馬里蘭共和國，並在當地設立一個[[軍事基地|軍事基地]]；德國最終並沒有這樣做，而是在吉布地建立[[海軍|海軍]]基地<ref name="german-foreign-policy.com">{{cite web | url=http://www.german-foreign-policy.com/de/fulltext/20084 | title=www.german-foreign-policy.com | publisher=www.german-foreign-policy.com | date= | accessdate=2012-05-29 | archive-date=2016-03-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305094854/http://www.german-foreign-policy.com/de/fulltext/20084 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.uni-kassel.de/fb5/frieden/regionen/Somalia/dieterich.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-11-27 |archive-date=2010-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100508130334/http://www.uni-kassel.de/fb5/frieden/regionen/Somalia/dieterich.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author=Süddeutsche.de GmbH, Munich, Germany | url=http://www.sueddeutsche.de/politik/dschibuti-einer-der-heissesten-flecken-der-welt-1.313955 | title=Dschibuti - Einer der heißesten Flecken der Welt - Politik | publisher=sueddeutsche.de | date=2002-01-02 | accessdate=2012-05-29 | archive-date=2019-06-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616190803/https://www.sueddeutsche.de/politik/dschibuti-einer-der-heissesten-flecken-der-welt-1.313955 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，德國海軍艦艇亦已撤離索馬利蘭[[柏培拉|柏培拉]]<ref name="german-foreign-policy.com"/>。2012年9月，德國政府在[[联合国大会|联合国大会]]關於索馬利亞問題的小型首腦會議上重申該國支持索馬利亞政府、領土完整和主權<ref name="Cosgmsos">{{cite web|title=Communiqué on Secretary-General's Mini-Summit on Somalia|url=http://www.un.org/News/Press/docs/2012/sg2187.doc.htm|publisher=United Nations|accessdate=7 August 2013|archive-date=2013-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019134114/http://www.un.org/News/Press/docs/2012/sg2187.doc.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2010年2月，有傳[[以色列|以色列]]可能會承認索馬里蘭<ref name="unpo">{{cite web | url=http://www.unpo.org/content/view/10712/236/ | title=Somaliland: Israel says ready to recognize Somaliland | publisher=UNPO | date=2010-02-12 | accessdate=2012-05-29 | archive-date=2020-04-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427041243/https://unpo.org/content/view/10712/236/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=No Author |url=http://jimmatimes.com/article/Latest_News/Latest_News/Somalia_Israel_to_recognize_Somaliland_independence/33268 |title=Somalia: Israel to recognize Somaliland independence |publisher=Jimma Times |accessdate=2012-05-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315172722/http://jimmatimes.com/article/Latest_News/Latest_News/Somalia_Israel_to_recognize_Somaliland_independence/33268 |archivedate=2012-03-15 }}</ref>，但傳言已被證實是謠傳<ref name="jungeweltde">{{cite web | url=http://www.jungewelt.de/2010/07-01/012.php | title=junge Welt – die linke Tageszeitung. Nachrichten und Hintergründe | publisher=Jungewelt.de | date=2012-05-24 | accessdate=2012-05-29 | archive-date=2010-07-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100703054722/http://www.jungewelt.de/2010/07-01/012.php | dead-url=no }}</ref>；同時，有指索馬里蘭和以色列軍火商曾[[走私|走私]]軍火<ref name="jungeweltde"/>。2011年，南非和[[坦尚尼亞|坦尚尼亞]]兩國的[[外長|外長]]均指他們不準備承認索馬里蘭，希望索馬里繼續為單一統治全境的國家<ref>{{cite news | date=13 August 2011 | title=SA, Tanzania don't recognise Somaliland | url=http://www.timeslive.co.za/local/2011/08/13/sa-tanzania-don-t-recognise-somaliland | newspaper=Times Live | accessdate=13 October 2014 | archive-date=2019-06-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190624193150/https://www.timeslive.co.za/local/2011/08/13/sa-tanzania-don-t-recognise-somaliland | dead-url=no }}</ref>；2012年，南非和衣索比亞在聯合國大会關於索馬利亞問題的小型首腦會議上重申將繼續支持索馬利亞政府、領土完整和主權<ref name="Cosgmsos"/>。

2014年4月，英國{{link-en|謝菲爾德市議會|Sheffield City Council}}舉行關於是否承認索馬里蘭[[自決|自決]]權利的投票，是首個舉行類似投票的市議會<ref name="Vshbsfiib"/>；投票不具有法律效力<ref name="Vshbsfiib">{{cite news | title=Somaliland Hails British Step Forward in Independence Bid | url=http://www.voanews.com/content/somaliland-hails-british-step-forward-in-independence-bid/1886918.html | accessdate=23 April 2014 | newspaper=VOA | date=5 April 2014 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023063050/http://www.voanews.com/content/somaliland-hails-british-step-forward-in-independence-bid/1886918.html | archive-date=2014-10-23 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>，英國政府以及國際社會仍承認索馬里蘭為索馬里的自治區<ref name="Tupmorttsep"/>。

2019年7月4日，因[[几内亚总统|几内亚总统]][[阿尔法·孔戴|阿尔法·孔戴]]日前邀请[[索马里兰总统|索马里兰的总统]][[繆斯·比希·阿卜迪|繆斯·比希·阿卜迪]]访问几内亚首都科纳克里，并为其举行欢迎仪式。索马里外交与国际合作部部长阿瓦德4日在摩加迪沙宣布，索马里同几内亚断绝外交关系。阿瓦德说，索马里作出这一决定是因为几内亚侵犯了索马里主权与统一。阿瓦德同时警告其他国家不要侵犯索马里的主权和统一<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2019-07/04/c_1124712285.htm |title=索马里宣布与几内亚断交 |access-date=2019-07-13 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713064800/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2019-07/04/c_1124712285.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2020年6月30日，媒體報導，[[索马里兰总统|索马里兰的总统]][[繆斯·比希·阿卜迪|繆斯·比希·阿卜迪]]將派遣[[索馬利蘭共和國駐台灣代表處|索馬利蘭共和國駐台灣代表處]]代表<ref>{{cite news|url=https://somalilandchronicle.com/2020/06/30/breaking-president-bihi-appoints-a-somaliland-representative-to-taiwan/|work=Somaliland Chronicle|title=Breaking President Bihi appoints a Somaliland representative to Taiwan|accessdate=2020-07-01|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228070054/https://somalilandchronicle.com/2020/06/30/breaking-president-bihi-appoints-a-somaliland-representative-to-taiwan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。7月1日，中華民國外交部長[[吳釗燮|吳釗燮]]正式宣布雙方互設代表處<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202007015011.aspx|work=中央社|title=吳釗燮宣布 台灣索馬利蘭互設代表處|accessdate=2020-07-01|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303075038/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202007015011.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，外交部公文中称索马里兰为“国家”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mofa.gov.tw/News_Content_M_2.aspx?n=8742DCE7A2A28761&s=2FF8BD1C90C68576 |title=我國宣布將與索馬利蘭共和國互設代表處 |access-date=2020-07-02 |archive-date=2020-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216233023/https://www.mofa.gov.tw/News_Content_M_2.aspx?n=8742DCE7A2A28761&s=2FF8BD1C90C68576 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，即表示索马里兰已得到中華民國的承认（参见[[中华民国与索马里兰关系|中华民国与索马里兰关系]]）<ref>{{cite web |title=难兄难弟 台湾与“索马里兰”互送秋波 |url=https://www.dw.com/zh/难兄难弟-台湾与索马里兰互送秋波/a-54016229 |website=德国之声 |accessdate=2020.6 |archive-date=2020-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819214505/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E9%9A%BE%E5%85%84%E9%9A%BE%E5%BC%9F-%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE%E4%B8%8E%E7%B4%A2%E9%A9%AC%E9%87%8C%E5%85%B0%E4%BA%92%E9%80%81%E7%A7%8B%E6%B3%A2/a-54016229 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

